{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">了解钠与钾的焰色反应的颜色。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">钠的焰色反应呈黄色，钾的焰色反应呈紫色。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">仪器：本生灯、试管、铂丝、蓝色钴玻璃、火柴。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">药品：氯化钾溶液、氯化钠溶液。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">1.分别取少量氯化钾溶液和氯化钠溶液于两支试管中，用铂丝蘸取氯化钠溶液，然后在本生灯上灼烧，观察实验现象；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">2.用另一根干净的铂丝蘸取氯化钾溶液，放在本生灯上灼烧，观察实验现象。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">1.火焰呈黄色；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">2.</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">火焰呈紫色。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}